divs: sighting detailsdriving from kirkland wa to duvall wa and observed flashes of light like a meteor or lightning. turned onto woodinville-duvall rd and observed more flashes and then three huge balls of light that were moving at tree top level. lights then began to twinkle\flash as we drove farther down the road. lost sight after about 1 mile.
trends: There has been one other sighting in Duvall
There were no other sightings in Duvall on or around December 20th 2011
Summary: Flashes like lightning, Three huge balls of twinkling light
